Package: secubox-rtty
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         secubox-core,
         rtty
Description: SecuBox Remote Terminal Access (rtty)
 Web-based remote terminal access module for SecuBox.
 Features:
  - rtty service control (start/stop/restart)
  - Active terminal session monitoring
  - Access token generation and management
  - Configuration editor (port, SSL, auth)
  - Embedded terminal web interface
  - Three-fold architecture (Components/Status/Access)
